ommand | Normalized Event | Notes |\\n    14→|---|---|---|---|\\n    15→| `sessionStart` | `session-start` | `SessionStart` | Session begins or resumes |\\n    16→| `sessionEnd` | `session-end` | `SessionEnd` | Session completes/terminated |\\n    17→| `userPromptSubmitted` | `user-prompt-submitted` | `TurnStart` | User submits prompt |\\n    18→| `agentStop` | `agent-stop` | `TurnEnd` | Agent finished responding |\\n    19→| `subagentStop` | `subagent-stop` | `SubagentEnd` | Subagent completed |\\n    20→| `preToolUse` | `pre-tool-use` | `nil` | Pass-through |\\n    21→| `postToolUse` | `post-tool-use` | `nil` | Pass-through |\\n    22→| `errorOccurred` | `error-occurred` | `nil` | Logging only |\\n    23→\\n    24→**Common stdin fields** (all hooks): `timestamp`, `cwd`, `sessionId`, `hookEventName`, `transcript_path`\\n    25→\\n    26→**Hook-specific fields**: `source`/`initialPrompt` (sessionStart), `reason` (sessionEnd), `prompt` (userPromptSubmitted), `toolName`/`toolArgs` (preToolUse/postToolUse), `toolResult` (postToolUse), `error` (errorOccurred)\\n    27→\\n    28→---\\n    29→\\n    30→## Step 0: Verify Hook stdin Format\\n    31→\\n    32→**Before writing code**, capture actual stdin JSON to confirm the common fields and `agentStop`/`subagentStop` format:\\n    33→\\n    34→```json\\n    35→{\\n    36→  \\\"version\\\": 1,\\n    37→  \\\"hooks\\\": {\\n    38→    \\\"sessionStart\\\": [{\\\"type\\\": \\\"command\\\", \\\"bash\\\": \\\"cat > /tmp/copilot-session-start.json\\\", \\\"timeoutSec\\\": 10}],\\n    39→    \\\"agentStop\\\": [{\\\"type\\\": \\\"command\\\", \\\"bash\\\": \\\"cat > /tmp/copilot-agent-stop.json\\\", \\\"timeoutSec\\\": 10}],\\n    40→    \\\"userPromptSubmitted\\\": [{\\\"type\\\": \\\"command\\\", \\\"bash\\\": \\\"cat > /tmp/copilot-user-prompt.json\\\", \\\"timeoutSec\\\": 10}]\\n    41→  }\\n    42→}\\n    43→```\\n    44→\\n    45→Place at `.github/hooks/copilot-setup.json`, run `copilot`, check `/tmp/copilot-*.json`. Confirm